			<div class="content" id="post-content-1986678">
									

<p>This is a real beaut of a rewrite. I do miss <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/sector-25">SRegan's old idea</a> of what a sector was &#8212; something like a geographical region where a bunch of secure facilities are located. I'm sure there's another term that would work just as well though.</p>
<p>This system is top-notch. Nice work, rewrite team!</p>

							</div>

								
					
